This is the OCF Git repository of its public Puppet configuration.

Git repository configuration:
mkdir puppet.git && cd puppet.git
chown staff:ocfstaff .
chmod g+swX .
git init --bare --shared=group
git config receive.fsckObjects true
git config receive.denyNonFastForwards true
Add Git update hook to check Puppet syntax
Add Git post-receive hook to deploy dev configuration
